com.vector.cfg.gen.core.bswmdmodel

Interface GIOptional<T extends GIModelObject>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>

    @NotThreadSafe
 @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
public interface GIOptional<T extends GIModelObject>
extends java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Interface for optional model objects.

    You can test a request before it will throw an exception, if the modelObject exists.

    This mechanism shall provide a compile time check for optional objects. The user must explicitly write an additional get() to see that this is optional.

    (c) Copyright Vctr Informatik GmbH. All Rights Reserved.
